    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, factory-original luster, and there are no chips, scratches, or dings to be found anywhere. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery, dashboard, and carpets showing zero signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that needs absolutely nothing.",
