    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained ride? This car is in good condition and is ready to take you on your next adventure! It has been cared for and performs solidly on the road, making it a great choice for anyone seeking a dependable vehicle that still looks and drives great.",
