    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The exterior has significant paint fading, several noticeable dents, and some rust starting to show on the wheel arches. Inside, the upholstery shows heavy wear and there are several non-functional electronic components, including the radio and power windows. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention for a persistent oil leak and a suspension that needs a complete overhaul. It is drivable, but I strongly recommend a full mechanical inspection before any long-distance trips.",
      "price": 4500.0,
