    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both performance and proven reliability. Meticulously maintained and showing clear evidence of responsible ownership, it offers a refined cabin environment and a robust mechanical profile. This selection represents an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that balances sophisticated aesthetics with enduring structural integrity.",
