    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect balance of performance and daily utility. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with minimal creasing, and all electronic features\u2014including the high-fidelity sound system, navigation, and dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule and a recent full-synthetic oil change, filter replacement, and brake inspection. It has been garage-kept, comes from a smoke-free environment, and has a clean title. This is a dependable, well-cared-for car that drives as beautifully as it looks, providing a premium experience for its next owner without the need for immediate repairs or detailing.",
